title: Lens 1-1 Paris Saint-Germain (3-4 on pens): Safonov the hero in Coupe de France tie
description: Paris Saint-Germain goalkeeper Matvey Safonov saved two spot-kicks to send his side through to the next round of the Coupe de France after beating Lens 4-3 on penalties.
